                        <div class="post-faq-card">
                            <h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-4">Why are some clinics dramatically cheaper than others?</h4>
                            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Significantly lower prices almost always reflect one or more compromises: unqualified technicians performing the procedure, reused instruments, inadequate graft preservation, reduced procedure time that limits quality control, or a high-volume assembly-line model where patient outcomes are secondary to throughput. These compromises are invisible on the day but visible in the result.</p>
